 <section id="TechInfo.Filesystems.Comparison">
  <title>Comparison of Supported File Systems</title>

  <para>
   &caasp; &this-version; exclusively supports the file system types Btrfs
   and OverlayFS. A read-only Btrfs file system is used for the root
   partition which enables transactional updates.
  </para>

  <para>
   <simplelist>
    <member><emphasis role="bold">+</emphasis> supported</member>
    <member><emphasis role="bold">–</emphasis> unsupported</member>
   </simplelist>
  </para>

